title: Gracious 959 Sq. Ft. apartment in Frisco
posting_body: ['Modera Frisco Square', 'Property Address', '5995 Gordon Street, ,', 'Frisco, TX, 75034', '<URL>', 'Stretch out in your spacious new 1 bed 1.5 bath apartment at Modera Frisco Square.', 'This popular floor plan is now available for as low as $1,697.00 a month.', 'Give us a call or stop by to check out all of the amenities.', 'Floor Plan Details', 'Name: A20L', '1 Bedrooms / 1.5 Bathrooms', '959 Sq.', 'Ft.', '$1,697.00', 'Community Amenities', 'Controlled Guest Access Technology', 'Game Room with Wi-Fi, Shuffleboard, and Coffee Bar', 'Sparkling Pool with Chaise Lounge Seating + Gathering Areas', 'HIIT-Inspired Fitness Studio with Yoga/Pilates Room + Group Fitness Area', 'Dedicated Resident Bike Storage', 'Close to the Dallas North Tollway and Cotton Gin Road', 'Multiple Peaceful Green Spaces Throughout the Community', 'Controlled-Access Parking', 'Pet Spa', 'Co-Working Space + Conference Area', 'Minutes to Frisco Commons Park and Dash Tracks Disc Golf Park', 'Elegant Lobby', 'Complimentary Wi-Fi in social spaces', 'Cozy Clubroom with Luxe Gathering Areas, Sleek Fireplace + HDTV', 'Golf Simulator', 'Unique Art Throughout Community', 'Pet Policy', 'We love your furry companions and welcome up to two per apartment home.', 'While we are huge fans of individuality (and the exotic), we have to ask that exotic pals, such as skunks and ferrets, find happy homes with a friend or family member.', 'Please note that we reserve the right to disallow certain aggressive breeds of dogs and aquariums as per our pet addendum.', 'Please contact our leasing office for information.', 'Property Contact', 'show contact info', 'show contact info', 'ADA ACCESSIBLE']
